2004-02-26  Olaf Weber  <olaf@infovore.xs4all.nl>

	* tangle.ch: Treat pool files as binary files, not text files
	(matters on some platforms).

	* pooltype.ch: Treat pool files as binary files, not text files
	(matters on some platforms).

